# Regenerated fresh by `npx expo prebuild --clean` on every Codemagic build.
# A committed copy made EAS tooling detect this project as bare workflow for
# Android while iOS (no committed ios/) stayed managed, a split-brain state
# that broke runtime version resolution for OTA updates.
